_sText: First try at making a good map, so dont flame me if you dont like it. Please give me constructive feedback (tips) on how I can improve this map if you have something to complain about. Also, bots dont work so well on this for some reason, so, dont hate me cause they dont work. This map is meant for omg-I-have-to-sleep-but-ill-just-get-one-game-in times, not for huge online death matches.
